{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775858847634,"sessionID":"ses_286917275ffeVx3USWNLrvoLju","part":{"id":"prt_d796f8f52001i897YVzlhGRnF7","messageID":"msg_d796f67ec001TB8aUQ0rmXPs6Q","sessionID":"ses_286917275ffeVx3USWNLrvoLju","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-7b74cdb8d54540df81c7a2638f56258e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-015/tasks.md","offset":700},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-015/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n700: - JWT authentication works correctly for all /api/* endpoints\n701: - Path sanitization prevents workspace escape\n702: - Error responses follow consistent format\n703: - Graceful shutdown works correctly\n704: - Security tests demonstrate robustness\n705: - No race conditions under concurrent load\n706: - Performance benchmarks meet requirements\n707: - CLI binary builds and runs correctly\n708: - Documentation is complete and accurate\n709: \n710: ### Dependencies\n711: - Go 1.24+\n712: - `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` v1.10.0+\n713: - `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` v5.2.0+\n714: - `k8s.io/klog/v2` v2.130.1+\n715: - `github.com/stretchr/testify` v1.9.0+ (Testing)\n716: \n717: ### Blocked By\n718: - None (design stage ST-3 completed)\n719: \n720: ### Blocks\n721: - AR-009 (Router HTTP 反向代理核心) - Router may integrate with PicoD for code execution\n722: - AR-011 (Router JWT 认证与签发) - JWT authentication integration\n723: - Production deployment with PicoD as code execution engine\n724: \n725: ### Notes\n726: - PicoD uses RS256 signing algorithm for JWT authentication\n727: - Public key is loaded from `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` environment variable\n728: - Default port: 8080\n729: - Default timeout: 60 seconds\n730: - Maximum request body size: 32 MiB\n731: - Workspace jail enforced through path sanitization\n732: - All 