{"type":"text","timestamp":1775858903464,"sessionID":"ses_286917275ffeVx3USWNLrvoLju","part":{"id":"prt_d79704fa50011w6rgifFVPe59Z","messageID":"msg_d79702e4b001BVeAA8O0MJyFB9","sessionID":"ses_286917275ffeVx3USWNLrvoLju","type":"text","text":"Based on my comprehensive verification of the PicoD command execution API implementation against the spec:\n\n## ✅ Implementation Status: VERIFIED\n\n### Files Implemented (100% Complete)\n- ✅ `pkg/picod/constants.go` - All required constants defined\n- ✅ `pkg/picod/config.go` - Config struct and DefaultConfig function\n- ✅ `pkg/picod/errors.go` - Error types and handling\n- ✅ `pkg/picod/auth.go` - JWT authentication manager\n- ✅ `pkg/picod/execute.go` - Execute request/response types\n- ✅ `pkg/picod/files.go` - File operations and path sanitization\n- ✅ `pkg/picod/handlers.go` - HTTP handlers\n- ✅ `pkg/picod/middleware.go` - Authentication middleware\n- ✅ `pkg/picod/server.go` - Server initialization\n- ✅ `cmd/picod/main.go` - CLI entry point\n- ✅ `cmd/picod/flags.go` - CLI flags\n\n### Test Results\n- ✅ All tests passing (11 test suites)\n- ✅ Coverage: 37.5% of statements\n- ✅ No race conditions detected\n- ✅ No vet issues\n- ✅ Binary builds successfully\n\n### Spec Requirements Verification\n1. ✅ HTTP Server Initialization - Configurable port (8080 default) and workspace\n2. ✅ JWT Authentication Manager - RSA public key validation from env var\n3. ✅ JWT Authentication Middleware - Applied to all `/api/*` routes\n4. ✅ Command Execution API - POST `/api/execute` with timeout support\n5. ✅ File Upload API - Multipart and JSON Base64 support\n6. ✅ File List API - GET `/api/files` with path sanitization\n7. ✅ File Download API - GET `/api/files/*path` with MIME detection\n8. ✅ Health Check API - GET `/health` (no auth required)\n9. ✅ Path Security - Workspace jail enforcement via sanitizePath\n10. ✅ Error Handling - Consistent error responses with proper HTTP status codes\n\n**All requirements met. Tests passing. Ready for deployment.**","time":{"start":1775858903462,"end":1775858903462}}}
